Improving our services
Manage your opinions on our products, services, courses or content
Create a file of customers and prospects
Send newsletters, solicitations and promotional messages by email
Respond to your requests for information
Comply with legal obligations applicable to our business
Develop statistics (navigation, the audience of the Site/Application, etc.) and improve the functionalities of the Site/Application through the deposit of audience measurement cookies
Broadcast personalized advertising through the deposit of advertising cookies
Allow you to simulate your income
Locate you in order to allow you to find a Driver or a User more easily
Manage incidents
Fighting fraud
Detect excessive or abusive cancellations by Users
Manage requests to exercise rights
